::Prowl::

Prowl looks at the leaving Ramhorn, one eyebrow raised. Having been an 
autobot in his past life, he understands some of the words.

He shruggs. War causes tensions. Ramhorn probably just needed to cool off. He 
turns back to Iron Raptor, smiling at her comment, "Let's go. If the meeting 
hasn't ended yet, we might be able to get there in time."
